{"tid":1257264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IG用戶上載性感美女照　疑似警方IG讚好照片","createTime":"2019-06-25T12:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T08:26:45.000Z","uid":66271,"like":115,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"792c2e79394c1cc92c2ce81ecc268d9e791463f1","tid":1257264,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2380000/2384928/police_thumb_20190625_cc_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2380000%2F2384928%2Fpolice_thumb_20190625_cc_1024.jpg&h=2c01dacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日的反送中示威活動中，警方不時透過社交平台發放信息，成為市民及記者接收警方信息的重要渠道。不過，有眼利網民發現，有疑似警方Instagram的「小編」，於Instagram讚好一張身材姣好的性感美女相片。TOPick記者正向警察公共關係科了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n一位名為「mov850908a」的網民，在Instagram上載了一張身材姣好的性感美女相片，有眼利的網民發現，這張相片竟然被「hongkongpoliceforce」讚好。TOPick記者翻查該帳戶，有關圖片是在今日（6月25日）凌晨3時許上載的，而截至今日下午5時許已有2.6萬多個讚好，但卻找不到「hongkongpoliceforce」的蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e21b3dbf2dcbc89fa5e180fd3f33156b7626f4","tid":1257264,"uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"阿sir做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25739c9a454ba0ef83dc00c8f90d5d25d149e691","tid":1257264,"uid":152589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"like野唔洗你教"},{"pid":"0dc126c77a992f72feca70468d922e086490bf36","tid":1257264,"uid":256246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"係咪毅進咁岩IT堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64013b5efe9a2628225632c14c3dad63413e96dd","tid":1257264,"uid":22624,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"咁阿sir都有丁權嘅"},{"pid":"2a88ab382eb4